author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Commercial Bank Of Dubai FY Profit Flat at 1 Bln Dirhams
text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - COMMERCIAL BANK OF DUBAI:
* FY NET PROFIT 1 ‍​BILLION DIRHAMS VERSUS 1 BILLION DIRHAMS YEAR AGO
* FY OPERATING INCOME OF 2.64 BILLION DIRHAMS, UP 7.3 PERCENT YEAR ON YEAR
* BOARD PROPOSES FY CASH DIVIDEND OF 20 PERCENT OF CAPITAL * AS OF END-DEC 2017, CUSTOMERS’ DEPOSITS STAND AT 48.41 BILLION DIRHAMS, UP 10.6 PERCENT YEAR-ON-YEAR
* AS OF END-DEC 2017, NET LOANS AND ADVANCES STAND AT 47.28 BILLION DIRHAMS, UP 12.7 PERCENT YEAR-ON-YEAR Source:( bit.ly/2E8YDfj ) Further company coverage:
